title: Knowledge Is Not Power, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO49
description: Remember those Public Service Announcements that proclaimed, "Knowledge is Power?" Andy Frisella says it's not true. Education is not complete without experience and application. Mere information will do nothing for you. You've got to put it into action.
